	[build int] Drop unuseful "fs2c --no-cgen".

	* fs2c (feed-gperf): Don't take ‘no-cgen?’; always generate C.
	(fs2c/qop): Update call to ‘feed-gperf’.
	(main): Drop ‘no-cgen’ from options spec.

